

Tar-gz with parallel compression:
	Compression:
	 $ tar c -C /path/to... myDirectory/ | pigz > fileName.tar.gz
	Decompression:
	 $ unpigz -c fileName.tar.gz | tar xv
		Options:
			--strip-components=N : Avoid N parent path levels.
